reaction) using proton energies close to the reaction
threshold. Target layer was chosen thick enough.
-Using 7Li(P,N) reaction and proton energy very close
to the threshold energy 1.881 MeV practically symmet-

Required proton energy conditions and neutron
spectra integrated over solid angle of sample
were determined in TOF measurement before activation.

of 6 mm diameter, heated to 1000 Celsius degree for 3
hours, put in a thin al foil. Masses of Ca-C-O3
samples are in the range 59.6 - 79.6 milligram
